00:19:42.531 --> 00:19:47.611
whether you are a passionate driver who goes everywhere by car or someone

00:19:47.611 --> 00:19:51.811
who doesn’t even have a driving licence, I hope it has made you think about

00:19:51.851 --> 00:19:56.491
parking, and the way in which cities are planned, in a slightly different way.

